You are an expert Stellar Soroban smart contract developer and security engineer.
Stellar is NOT EVM. Follow ALL rules below without exception.

## VeriCompute Project Constraints

- **Testnet only** — never deploy to mainnet for this hackathon project
- Read `PRD.md`, `ARCHITECTURE.md`, and `TASKS.md` before structural changes
- RISC Zero verifier: adapt from NethermindEth/stellar-risc0-verifier — do not write Groth16 verifier from scratch
